'''瓦鰈科'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|''Poecilopsettidae''}}），有分類作'''瓦鰈亞科'''（{{lang|la|''Poecilopsettinae''}}），是[[輻鰭魚綱|輻鰭魚綱]][[鰈亞目|鰈亞目]]的其中一科。

==分類==
瓦鰈科其下有三個屬<ref>{{cite journal | author = J. A. Cooper and F. Chapleau | year = 1998 | title = Monophyly and intrarelationships of the family Pleuronectidae (Pleuronectiformes), with a revised classification | journal = Fish. Bull. | volume = 96 | issue = 4 | pages = 686–726}}</ref><ref>{{ITIS | taxon = Poecilopsettidae | id = 615935 | accessdate = 2013-02-15 }}</ref>：
===馬來鰈屬（''Marleyella'' <small>Fowler, 1925</small>）===
*[[絲鰭馬來鰈|絲鰭馬來鰈]] (''Marleyella bicolorata'')
*[[馬爾地夫馬來鰈|馬爾地夫馬來鰈]](''Marleyella maldivensis'')
===線鰭瓦鰈屬（''Nematops'' <small>Günther, 1880</small>）===
*[[大鱗線鰭瓦鰈|大鱗線鰭瓦鰈]] (''Nematops grandisquama'')
*[[大手線鰭瓦鰈|大手線鰭瓦鰈]] (''Nematops macrochirus'')
*[[小口線鰭瓦鰈|小口線鰭瓦鰈]] (''Nematops microstoma'')
*[[細鱗線鰭瓦鰈|細鱗線鰭瓦鰈]](''Nematops nanosquama'')
===瓦鰈屬（''Poecilopsetta'' <small>Günther, 1880</small>）===
*[[白斑瓦鰈|白斑瓦鰈]] (''Poecilopsetta albomaculata'')
*[[比恩氏瓦鰈|比恩氏瓦鰈]](''Poecilopsetta beanii'')
*[[黑斑瓦鰈|黑斑瓦鰈]] (''Poecilopsetta colorata'') 
*[[高背瓦鰈|高背瓦鰈]](''Poecilopsetta dorsialta'')
*[[夏威夷瓦鰈|夏威夷瓦鰈]] (''Poecilopsetta hawaiiensis'')
*[[無刺瓦鰈|無刺瓦鰈]](''Poecilopsetta inermis'')
*[[大頭瓦鰈|大頭瓦鰈]](''Poecilopsetta macrocephala'')
*[[多輻瓦鰈|多輻瓦鰈]](''Poecilopsetta multiradiata'')
*[[南非瓦鰈|南非瓦鰈]] (''Poecilopsetta natalensis'')
*[[諾氏瓦鰈|諾氏瓦鰈]] (''Poecilopsetta normani'')
*[[大胸瓦鰈|大胸瓦鰈]](''Poecilopsetta pectoralis'')
*[[雙斑瓦鰈|雙斑瓦鰈]] (''Poecilopsetta plinthus'')
*[[長體瓦鰈|長體瓦鰈]] (''Poecilopsetta praelonga'')
*[[沃氏瓦鰈|沃氏瓦鰈]](''Poecilopsetta vaynei'')
*[[桑給巴爾瓦鰈|桑給巴爾瓦鰈]] (''Poecilopsetta zanzibarensis'')

